Description: ROS Noetic desktop bundle for Ubuntu Noble
 This package installs a bundled ROS Noetic desktop tree under /opt/ros/noetic.
 It is intended as a practical Noble build artifact, not as a replacement for
 the official split ROS Debian package set.
